if you can't do the time.

00:12.490 --> 00:14.927
- This is stupid.
- Quit saying "stupid."

00:15.015 --> 00:16.625
That's why your friends
are out riding bikes

00:16.712 --> 00:19.193
and I'm in here riding you.

00:19.280 --> 00:23.414
Hey, that kid said, "In 1982,
Columbus sailed the ocean blue."

00:23.501 --> 00:25.764
That doesn't give you the right
to call him stupid.

00:25.851 --> 00:29.942
I may have said it, but,
everybody else was thinking it.

00:30.030 --> 00:31.248
Well, you need to bite
your tongue

00:31.335 --> 00:34.208
and roll your eyes,
just like I do.

00:34.295 --> 00:35.774
My dad says
that's the reason

00:35.861 --> 00:38.299
this country's going
to hell in a hand basket.

00:38.386 --> 00:41.519
Your dad sounds
like a piece of work.

00:41.606 --> 00:43.391
Notice I said "piece of work"
instead of what

00:43.478 --> 00:45.828
I was really thinking.

00:45.915 --> 00:47.873
He says, "How else
are stupid people

00:47.960 --> 00:49.092
gonna learn
if we don't call them

00:49.179 --> 00:50.354
on their stupid stuff."

00:50.441 --> 00:51.616
Oh, I love
when the parents help.

00:51.703 --> 00:55.490
Hey, sweetie,
about ready to go?

00:55.577 --> 00:58.797
Uh, hello, officer.
I'm glad you came.

00:58.884 --> 01:01.322
This young man
needs to be taught a lesson.

01:01.409 --> 01:03.237
- You called the cops on me?
- 'Yes.'

01:03.324 --> 01:04.760
