another boy's feelings.

01:26.999 --> 01:30.525
He said, "In 1982, Columbus
sailed the ocean blue."

01:30.612 --> 01:32.440
Well, just 'cause
a kid's stupid doesn't mean

01:32.527 --> 01:33.571
