of senseless animals.

18:22.884 --> 18:23.885
Hey, Vinny.

18:23.972 --> 18:25.016
Dwight, where the hell you been

18:25.104 --> 18:26.148
you inbred bastard?

18:26.235 --> 18:28.194
We're sitting here
for 45 minutes.

18:28.281 --> 18:31.806
Don't you start in with me,
you Italian fireplug.

18:31.893 --> 18:34.548
You know I hate driving my rig
in this godforsaken town.

18:34.635 --> 18:36.680
Yeah, yeah. Welcome to life
in the big city.

18:36.767 --> 18:39.727
Enjoy our toothbrushes
and indoor plumbing.

18:41.468 --> 18:42.730
Is this the guy?

18:42.817 --> 18:45.167
My investment partner,
Officer Michael Biggs.

18:45.254 --> 18:47.387
Look, uh, this is a lot
of money for me.

18:47.474 --> 18:48.910
You sure
this is a good investment?

18:48.997 --> 18:50.999
Money in the bank.
Enough for ten birds.

18:51.086 --> 18:52.653
Five boys and five girls.

18:52.740 --> 18:54.307
Look, I already told you, grease
ball.

18:54.394 --> 18:56.222
You only need one stud cock

18:56.309 --> 18:58.006
and the rest breeding hens.

18:58.093 --> 19:00.748
It ain't like any of them is
looking for their soul mate.

19:00.835 --> 19:02.750
Don't push me, dueling banjos.

19:02.837 --> 19:04.143
Just pick us out some good birds

19:04.230 --> 19:07.494
and get back
to your cousin-wife.

19:07.581 --> 19:09.887
Hey, I scraped something
bigger than you off my boot

19:09.974 --> 19:12.412
this morning, and it smelled
better than you, too.

19:12.499 --> 19:14.153
When did you start
wearing shoes?

19:14.240 --> 19:17.156
Did your pappy go to town
and sell a pig?

19:18.592 --> 19:21.029
No. I shaved off
your mama's mustache

19:21.116 --> 19:24.293
and sold it to a wig store.

19:24.380 --> 19:26.339
Hang on a second. I-I thought
you guys were friends.

19:26.426 --> 19:31.039
We are. I'd take a bullet
for this baldheaded little wop.

19:31.126 --> 19:33.433
That goes double for me,
you dumb-ass cracker.

19:33.520 --> 19:35.478
By the way, you got
that 100 bucks you owe me?

19:35.565 --> 19:37.828
- I do now.
- Hey!

19:37.915 --> 19:39.482
Or we could double down.

19:39.569 --> 19:40.918
Let's roll, Jethro.

19:41.005 --> 19:42.398
Say, "One, two, three, go."

19:42.485 --> 19:43.791
One, two, three, go.

19:43.878 --> 19:45.488
Guys, I'm not really sure
about this.

19:45.575 --> 19:48.317
Hey, hee-haw,
is that your truck being towed?

19:48.404 --> 19:50.363
No, I ain't falling
for that one again.

19:50.450 --> 19:52.626
You know, maybe I should just
put this in a low-risk CD.

19:52.713 --> 19:55.498
You know, low-risk, minimal
return. No arm-wrestling!

20:01.809 --> 20:03.506
